---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'June 22, 2026';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Now"
  description="What Hugo Esposito-Farese is currently working on, learning, and thinking about."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-50 mb-3">Now</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 font-mono">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-10 max-w-xl">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Building</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>
              <a href="/projects/42ai-assistant" class="text-zinc-200 hover:text-white underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">42 AI Assistant</a> —
              iterating based on feedback from ~30 students at 42 Paris. Thinking about whether to open source it or build a web version.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>
              This website — my public build log.
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Learning</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>42 Paris core curriculum — C, Unix, algorithms, systems programming.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>How to talk to users and figure out if something is a real product versus a useful personal tool.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-blue-400 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Prompt engineering and working with LLM APIs — specifically how to build useful tools without removing the learning from the user.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Reading</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span><em class="text-zinc-300">Zero to One</em> — Peter Thiel</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Paul Graham essays — working through the archive chronologically.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Thinking about</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>What the right first business for me looks like. Leaning towards something I could build alone, with clear distribution, that solves a problem I understand deeply.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 mt-2.5 shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Whether AI tools for developer education are a real market or just a toy category.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-700 mt-14">
      Inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors">nownownow.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
